#

Caprese Salad

10 min
$10
320 kcal
Difficulty: 10%
Servings: 2

Allergens:

Dairy

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianGluten-Free

Cuisine:

Italian

Course:

Appetizer

Tags:

SaladAppetizerQuick

Description

A refreshing salad with creamy mozzarella, ripe tomatoes, and fragrant basil, perfect for a light meal.

Ingredients

  • fresh mozzarella: 8 oz
  • ripe tomatoes: 2 large
  • fresh basil leaves: 1 cup
  • balsamic glaze: 3 tbsp
  • olive oil: 2 tbsp
  • salt: to taste
  • black pepper: to taste
